      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and replacement of the rod bearings. The suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers for precise damping control, and the braking system remains firm with stainless steel braided lines. While the exterior displays honest patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain synchronized for peak performance.",
